DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

90-2537. Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Sack.

Sua sponte, the one-year suspension of Robert H. Sack, Attorney Registration No. 0010178, stayed in Cincinnati Bar Assn. v. Sack (1991), 60 Ohio St.3d 37, 572 N.E.2d 685, is immediately imposed; this cause is referred to the Office of Disciplinary Counsel; and this matter is referred to the Attorney General for collection.

Douglas and Wright, JJ., would immediately suspend Sack indefinitely and notify all courts of this suspension.
